This is a git repo


-> instal git on your pc
	+> linux (apt-get install git)
-> create acount git hub
-> create repository on git hub
	+> git init
	+> git config user.name "your name"
	+> git config user.email "your email can everything email"
	+> git add your file
	+> git commit -m "commit for you file"
	+> git remote add origin your addres github
	+> git push origin master


-> install module on project folder with npm
	+> npm init
	+> npm install -save huejay
	+> npm install -save hue-module
	+> npm install -save express
	+> npm install -save body-parser
-> for handler view node can use handlebars
	+> npm install -save hbs
-> for auto restart file node js instal nodemon
	+> npm install --save nodemon -g